#Kai
So An, you don't have the burden yourself too hard with the responsibility to tell people they're about to die.[p]
I gave you that eye because even as a Death's Messenger i can't undo death, even just the death of an eye.[p]
It was meant to be something to help you, no one else. God will determine each soul's end day by putting the death mark on them and us Death's messengers can see it as the black feathers.[p]
You're just a poor human who got yourself into this madness because the kidnappers beat you up in the temple of the Gods of Death.[p]
Which angered Hell King enough to give me a split oppoturnity to save you out. [p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Beside, i don't think the best way to help someone preparing for their death is to tell them when they're about to die.[p]
I think the best way is to help them enjoy life as best they can. [p]
You loved your father so much when he's alive and i know he felt that too.What happened to him wasn't your fault. [p]
And even when you think that's your responsibilities as a nurse with this power, you have me now, you're not alone.[p]
So cheer up. For both the patients and yourself.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

